title: 130: Bad body, good player, stars returning in NFL
itunes:title: 130: Bad body, good player, stars returning in NFL
description:
Former NFL scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the upcoming slate of NFL and college football games. The duo talks about NFL teams getting healthy as their best players return. Also, which great players don't exactly have bodies of steel? DJ and Bucky finally make their final push to assert themselves in the college football pick 'em challenge.
